title: The 20YA | Event Basics
body_text:
I'm putting this massive event in the category of ECD 100, ECD 200, and the 10YA. The 20YA was never even a thought especially in those long-ago but cherished early years, yet it approaches at rocket speed - who's in?
REGISTRATION IS OPEN 🙂
